Adverse Events Table by Body System and Severity/Toxicity

Source: R/adae_utils.R
build_adae_by_sev_tox.Rd

Adverse Events Table by Body System and Severity/Toxicity

Usage

build_adae_by_sev_tox(
  adsl,
  df_adae,
  colsby = "ARM",
  filter_cond = NULL,
  grade_val = "AESEV",
  class_val = "AESOC",
  term_val = "AEDECOD",
  default_view = TRUE
)

Arguments

adsl

(data.frame)
ADSL dataset.

df_adae

(data.frame)
ADAE dataset.

colsby

(character)
Variable used to split table into columns.

filter_cond

(character)
Filtering condition required for df_adae.

grade_val

(character)
AE Severity or AE Toxicity Grade i.e. AESEV or AETOXGR

class_val

(character)
System Organ Class/Body System Class i.e. AESOC or AEBODSYS

term_val

(character)
Dictionary Derived Term i.e. AEDECOD or AETERM

default_view

(logical)
TRUE displays values of grade_val into columns.

Value

An rtable object

See also

Other adae_utils: add_adae_flags(), build_adae_summary()

Examples


library(clinTables)
library(rtables)
#> Loading required package: formatters
#> Loading required package: magrittr
#> Warning: package 'magrittr' was built under R version 4.1.3
adsl <- random.cdisc.data::cadsl
adae <- random.cdisc.data::cadae

tbl <- build_adae_by_sev_tox(
  adsl = adsl,
  df_adae = adae,
  colsby = "ARM",
  grade_val = "AESEV",
  class_val = "AESOC",
  term_val = "AEDECOD",
  default_view = TRUE
)

# \dontrun{
tt_to_flextable(tbl)
